result.title: Receiving wrong answer on submission but right answer on codeforces custom test ide
result.content:
I just submitted http://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/515/C , in my compiler "dev c++" it works perfectly and the initial tests are correct, it retruned wrong answer on test 1 when I submitted so I tested it in the custom test where I'm sure I put the exact same code, it returns right answer there as well but it gives wrong answer only on submission... can anyone help me and explain what is the problem here ?

for test case 1234 any compiler gives 33222 but on submission it gives 322. http://ideone.com/9DYs3n : Here's my code can somebody help!
